casebody.data:
James McAndrew, plaintiff in error, vs. The Augusta Mutual Loan Association, defendant in error. Jackson, Judge.

The record and bill of exceptions in this case failing to set out the petition, the rule, nisi, or rule absolute, or other final judgment of the court below, from which an appeal could be taken to this court, the writ of error is dismissed in accordance with the ruling in Bean Company vs. Hadley, delivered at the present term.
